 <section id="InfraPackArch.ArchIndependent.Kernel_Modules">
  <title>Kernel Modules</title>
  <!-- 2014-03-19, ke: bnc#869159 -->
  <!-- 2014-04-29, ke: find the same text in the SLED RN -->
  <para>
   An important requirement for every Enterprise operating system is the
   level of support a customer receives for his environment.  Kernel
   modules are the most relevant connector between hardware
   ("controllers") and the operating system.
  </para>

  <para>
   <!--  bnc#869159 -->
   For more information about the handling of kernel modules, see the
   &sle; Administration Guide.
  </para>
 </section>

